Package compiler.postfix

package compiler.postfix
Defines the classes and methods necessary to:
  • define the different Tokens that may appear in an expression
  • convert an infix expression to its equivalent postfix expression
  • produce the machine code that evaluates a postfix expression
Author:
Alex Mandelias
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    InfixToPostfix
    Defines the static method convertToPostfix(String) which converts the infix expression given as a String to its equivalent postfix expression represented by a list of Tokens.
    PostfixEvaluator
    Defines the static method evaluatePostfix(List, SymbolTable, SML_Copmiler) which returns the machine language instructions that evaluate the postfix expression.
    Token
    Wrapper for different tokens (strings) that can appear in infix and postfix expressions.
